If you have stoped using the launcher and the game keeps crashing when it is launched via KSP_64.exe, please update the crash log.

What are the specs of your system? CPU, RAM, GPU?
Would you mind adding a KSP.log or output_log.txt as well?
The KSP.log is located in your KSP install folder ( in your case: F:\Games\Kerbal Space Program\ ), the output _log.txt is located in ' %USERPROFILE%\AppData\LocalLow\Squad\Kerbal Space Program\ '

Please upload the log files to a filehoster and share a download link instead of copy&paste it in your post, to keep up the readability
